    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently maintained, making it a reliable choice for any driver. The engine starts up strong every time, and the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears, providing a comfortable ride on both city streets and highways. While the interior and exterior show some light signs of use consistent with its age, the overall mechanical health is excellent and it has plenty of life left. Buyers can expect a dependable vehicle that is ready to drive immediately without any urgent repairs needed.",
