      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable vehicle with a lot of life left? This car is in fair condition and ready for a new owner who appreciates a great value! While it shows some honest wear from its time on the road, it remains a solid choice for anyone looking for reliable transportation at an accessible price point. It\u2019s a fantastic opportunity to own a quality ride that\u2019s ready to keep on going!",
