    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Experience the pinnacle of automotive excellence with this showroom-condition masterpiece. Meticulously maintained and presenting in absolute mint condition, this vehicle offers a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast. From the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, factory-fresh interior, every detail reflects a standard of care that is simply unmatched. This is more than just a car; it is a testament to precision engineering preserved in its highest form. Fully inspected and ready for immediate delivery, it represents the absolute gold standard for pre-owned quality.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
